===Olympic Games===
[[File:Football at the 1912 Summer Olympics - Sweden squad.JPG|thumb|300px|Sweden at the [[Football at the 1912 Summer Olympics|1912 Summer Olympics]]]]
[[Football at the Summer Olympics]] was first played officially in [[Football at the 1908 Summer Olympics|1908]]. The Olympiads between 1896 and 1980 were only open for amateur players. The 1984 and 1988 tournaments were open to players with no appearances in the [[FIFA World Cup]]. Since [[Football at the 1992 Summer Olympics|1992 Olympics]], the football event was changed into a tournament for under-23 teams with a maximum of three [[List of overage players in Olympic football|overage players]]. See [[Sweden Olympic football team]] for competition record from 1984 until present day.
